View all standard units

Source: R/units.R
get_units.Rd

get_units() yields a dataframe with all standard units in Julia's Unitful package and added custom units by sdbuildR.

Usage

get_units()

Value

Dataframe with units in Julia

See also

Other units: convert_u(), drop_u(), get_regex_time_units(), get_regex_units(), model_units(), u(), unit_prefixes()

Examples
